*Finnish: [[piilottaa]]
*French: [[cacher]], [[dissimuler]], [[masquer]]
*Italian: [[nascondere]]
*Spanish: [[esconder]]

===Intransitive verb===
'''to hide''' (hides, [[hid]], [[hidden]], [[hiding]])

